<noinclude>
This is the '''Expense''' form, used to create and edit expense records
stored via [[Template:Expense]]. See [[Help:Receipts]].

An expense has 0 or 1 receipt (an uploaded file the parser used to
pre-fill these fields) and 0+ supporting documents (unparsed files such
as contracts or warranties). Parser pre-fills are highlighted; every
field is editable — the user is the verification step.
[[Category:Receipt forms]]
</noinclude><includeonly>{{{info|page name=Expense:<unique number;random;9>}}}
{{{for template|Expense}}}
{{{field|queue_id|hidden}}}
{| class="formtable"
|-
! Receipt file:
| {{{field|file|input type=tokens|max values=1|values from namespace=File}}} {{#receiptscanner_form_actions:}}
|-
! Date:
| {{{field|date|input type=date|mandatory}}}
|-
! Payee:
| {{{field|payee|input type=combobox|values from cargo=table=Expenses,field=payee|size=40}}}
|-
! Total:
| {{{field|total|input type=number}}} {{{field|currency|size=4|default={{#receiptscanner_system_currency:}}}}}
|-
! Exchange rate:
| {{{field|exchange_rate|input type=number|default=1}}} <small>({{#receiptscanner_system_currency:}} per 1 of the receipt's currency — only matters when the currency differs)</small>
|-
! Total in {{#receiptscanner_system_currency:}}:
| {{{field|total_system|input type=number}}}
|-
! Subtotal:
| {{{field|subtotal|input type=number}}}
|-
! Tax:
| {{{field|tax|input type=number}}}
|-
! Fees:
| {{{field|fees|input type=number}}}
|-
! Payment method:
| {{{field|payment_method|size=30}}}
|-
! Expense category:
| {{{field|expense_category|input type=combobox|delimiter=;|values={{#receiptscanner_categories:expense|;}}|size=40}}}
|-
! Assignee:
| {{{field|assignee|input type=combobox|values={{#receiptscanner_users:}}|default=current user|size=30}}} <small>(blank = company-wide)</small>
|-
! Supporting documents:
| {{{field|supplemental_files|input type=tokens|values from namespace=File}}}
|-
! Notes:
| {{{field|notes|input type=textarea|rows=4}}}
|}
{{{end template}}}

{{{standard input|save}}} {{{standard input|preview}}} {{{standard input|changes}}} {{{standard input|cancel}}}
</includeonly>
